75 A.3d 322 In the Matter of the Petition for REINSTATEMENT OF Cristine A. KEPPLE to the Bar of Maryland. Misc. Docket AG No. 34,

Sept. Term, 2013.

Court of Appeals of Maryland. Sept. 20, 2013.

ORDER

This matter came before this Court on the Petition for Reinstatement of Cristine A. Kepple and the response of Bar Counsel, and

The Court having considered the Petition and the Response of Bar Counsel, it is this 20th day of September, 2013

ORDERED, by the Court of Appeals of Maryland, that Cristine A. Kepple be, and she is hereby reinstated to the practice of law in this State; and it is further

ORDERED, that the Clerk of the court shall replace the name of Cristine A. Kepple upon the register of attorneys entitled to practice law in this State and certify that fact to the Trustees of the Client Protection Fund and the Clerks of all judicial tribunals in this State.
